items.title: 'We need Greenland': Trump repeats threat to annex Danish territory
items.description: The US president has repeatedly said he wants the island to become a part of the US.

items.title: South Korea's Lee Jae Myung meets China's Xi as he seeks to reset ties
items.description: Trade, regional security and Beijing's unofficial ban on Korean pop culture are on the agenda.

items.title: Thirty-two Cubans killed during US attack on Venezuela
items.description: Cuba's president said military and intelligence operatives were providing protection to captured leader Nicolás Maduro.

items.title: Trump warns new Venezuelan leader as Maduro set to appear in court
items.description: Trump said Venezuela's interim president Delcy Rodríguez could "pay a very big price, probably bigger than Maduro" if she "doesn't do what's right".

items.title: Police identify all 40 victims of Swiss bar fire
items.description: Among those killed by the blaze at Le Constellation is 16-year-old Swiss national Arthur Brodard, his mother confirms.
